data.description: Come see this beautiful home located in South West Medford, close to schools, shopping and medical. This home offers 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths and over 1300 sqft of livable space. With beautiful hardwood floors throughout the home and nice open spaces, potential abounds! The front living room has plenty of room for any desired arrangements. The spacious family room located in the back left corner of the home is a great size for you and the family to relax and enjoy the comforts of home. This home won't last long!  Call listing agent and schedule your tour today!
